oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Husky, Ferlin; Wells, Kitty;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1235) for an order placed by Concourse Concrete Company for 500 two color jumbos for a performance by Ferlin Husky and Kitty Wells at the Convention Hall Community Concourse in San Diego, California on June 6. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
